headline.print_headline: Cuba Not Returning to Capitalism Despite U.S. Deal: Castro's Daughter
headline.main: Cuba Not Returning to Capitalism Despite U.S. Deal: Castro's Daughter

lead_paragraph: Cuba will defend its socialist principles and will not return to capitalism just because it has agreed a detente with the United States, the daughter of President Raul Castro said, dispelling any notion that U.S. companies would be free to roll into Cuba.
